.webp",iq="/assets/devojeet-light-BAxsveSf.webp",sq="/assets/khushi-jindal-dark-CwvQIZ5Y.webp",aq="/assets/khushi-jindal-light-CPanXCBY.webp",rq="/assets/mayur-badgujar-dark-CMmAVvTe.webp",oq="/assets/mayur-badgujar-light-DlUv_w0Q.webp",lq="/assets/megha-pandey-dark-Cv0iSuq5.webp",cq="/assets/megha-pandey-light-4hye_lY1.webp",uq="/assets/monish-reddy-dark-aiKC2SYv.webp",dq="/assets/monish-reddy-light-CwNb3hzj.webp",hq="/assets/peeyush-tiwari-dark-3GWTTxxW.webp",fq="/assets/peeyush-tiwari-light-CHcjv7I-.webp",mq="/assets/radhika-dark-CSRyrno-.webp",pq="/assets/radhika-light-DLbztTRH.webp",gq="/assets/tejas-dherange-dark-knjN14H1.webp",yq="/assets/tejas-dherange-light-rVMtaYOE.webp",vq=[{id:"activity-1",question:"Building something real.",answer:'Not just "Hello World." In our live workshops, you build actual project components - the kind that go in portfolios and get noticed in interviews.You learn to read documentation, handle errors, and think through architecture. All the things that feel impossible until someone walks you through it once.'},{id:"activity-2",question:"Working under pressure.",answer:"Hackathons at ChaiCode aren't judged on polish - they're judged on thinking. Can you break a problem down? Can you collaborate under pressure? Can you ship something that works, even if it isn't perfect?"},{id:"activity-3",question:"Testing your fundamentals.",answer:"Our live quizzes test your understanding of DSA, system design concepts, and current industry trends in real time, against your own batchmates. The results will show you exactly where you stand."},{id:"activity-4",question:"Industry Talks",answer:"Candid conversations with working engineers -what they wish they knew in college, what hiring looks like in AI era, how to navigate a tech career."},{id:"activity-5",question:"Bounties",answer:"Win exclusive ChaiCode merchandise, cash bounties, and rewards by participating in community activities and events."}],bq=[{icon:xV,title:"Hands-on Experience",description:"You'll plan and run live events on campus. You'll manage logistics, handle an audience, and represent a platform trusted by hundreds of thousands of developers."},{icon:vV,title:"A Network That Opens Doors",description:"Every ChaiCode Ambassador is part of an active community where seniors with real industry experience answer real questions, share real opportunities."},{icon:CV,title:"Early Access",description:"Stay ahead of your batchmates. Consistently. Ambassadors get access to new courses, platform features, and learning resources before they go public."},{icon:jV,title:"Official Recognition",description:"You get a verified Campus Ambassador certificate and a public profile on the ChaiCode website. It's proof, not decoration. Visible to every student, employer, and mentor who visits."}],xq=[{icon:gV,title:"Apply",description:"Submit a short form with your college, technical background, and why you want to represent ChaiCode."},{icon:AV,title:"Profile Review",description:"Our team reviews every application, looking at your community engagement and communication style."},{icon:mV,title:"Interview",description:"Shortlisted applicants are invited for a brief interview to assess motivation, communication, and campus fit."},{icon:DV,title:"Onboarding",description:"Selected ambassadors are onboarded with resources, a private community channel, and their first campus brief."}],wq=[{id:1,name:"Peeyush Tiwari",university:"Quantum University",city:"Roorkee",state:"Uttrakhand",imageLight:fq,imageDark:hq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/peeyush-tiwari-a4b802319"}},{id:2,name:"G Monish Reddy",university:"Mohan Babu University",city:"Tirupati",state:"Andhra Pradesh",imageLight:dq,imageDark:uq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/technicalmonish/"}},{id:3,name:"Ankith Kumar",university:"Dr. Manmohan Singh Bengaluru City University",city:"Bengaluru",state:"Karnataka",imageLight:XU,imageDark:KU,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ankith-kumar-ab80a7240"}},{id:4,name:"Radhika",university:"J. C. Bose University of Science & Tech",city:"Faridabad",state:"Haryana",imageLight:pq,imageDark:mq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/radhika-a6a84837a"}},{id:5,name:"Ashish Singodiya",university:"Rajasthan Technical University",city:"Kota",state:"Rajasthan",imageLight:tq,imageDark:eq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ashish-singodiya-4802a8330"}},{id:6,name:"Megha Pandey",university:"Rungta College of Engineering",city:"Bhilai",state:"Chhattisgarh",imageLight:cq,imageDark:lq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/meghaapandeyy/"}},{id:7,name:"Mayur Badgujar",university:"SVKM's Institute of Technology",city:"Dhule",state:"Maharashtra",imageLight:oq,imageDark:rq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayurbadgujar03/"}},{id:8,name:"Khushi Jindal",university:"Netaji Subhas University of Technology",city:"Dwarka",state:"Delhi",imageLight:aq,imageDark:sq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/khushi-jindal"}},{id:9,name:"Tejas Dherange",university:"Vishwakarma Institute of Information Technology",city:"Pune",state:"Maharashtra",imageLight:yq,imageDark:gq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tejas-dherange-54a6a627b/"}},{id:10,name:"Ansh Mishra",university:"Oriental Institute Of Science & Technology",city:"Bhopal",state:"Madhya Pradesh",imageLight:JU,imageDark:QU,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ansh-mishraa/"}},{id:11,name:"Devojeet",university:"JayPee University",city:"Bulandshahr",state:"Uttar Pradesh",imageLight:iq,imageDark:nq,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/devo-jeet"}},{id:12,name:"Aditya Giri",university:"Oriental Institute of Science & Tech",city:"Bhopal",state:"Madhya Pradesh",imageLight:ZU,imageDark:YU,social:{linkedin:"https://www.linkedin.com/in/adityagiri14"}}],Cq=[{id:"language-and-prerequisites",question:"Language and Prerequisites?",answer:"The course will be taught in Hindi. Technical terms will remain in English. No prior programming experience is required. Basic computer skills and the willingness to learn are enough and explore beyond the course."},{id:"class-recordings",question:"Will I get recordings if I miss a class?",answer:"Yes. Every session is recorded and uploaded within 3-4 hours. You can watch it anytime until the course access is active."},{id:"course-access",question:"How long will I have access to the course content?",answer:"You get 3 years (1095 days) of access to all videos, notes, and resources."},{id:"masterji",question:"What is MasterJi and community?",answer:"MasterJi is our in-house platform where you track progress, give assignments to submit, provide code feedback and build projects. The community is hosted inside the MasterJi app. You will receive access before the cohort starts."},{id:"projects",question:"What projects will I build?",answer:"You will build real-world frontend, backend and full-stack projects that are portfolio-ready and reviewed by mentors."},{id:"timings",question:"What are the class timings?",answer:"Live classes are held on every Saturday & Sunday at 8:00 PM IST, with a bonus & doubt clearing session on every Thursday at 8:00 PM IST."},{id:"job-guarantee",question:"Is this course job-guaranteed?",answer:"No, this course does not offer a job guarantee. We provide a skill guarantee and make you capable enough to find opportunities on your own. If any referrals come during the cohort, they will be given only to selected high-performing learners inside MasterJi"},{id:"devices",question:"How many devices can I access the course on?",answer:"You can access the course on 2 devices—one laptop and one mobile. If the system detects account sharing, the account will be banned without notice, and course access will be permanently lost"},{id:"payment-methods",question:"What payment methods are supported?",answer:"All major payment options including UPI apps, Debit/ Credit cards, Netbanking from leading banks and popular wallets."},{id:"emi-options",question:"Are loan & EMI options available?",answer:"We do not recommend taking loan or EMI for this course as a student. If your finances are tight right now, you can start learning from our YouTube channel ChaiAurCode for free, it already covers a lot."},{id:"refund-policy",question:"What is the refund policy?",answer:"You can request a refund only upto 17th Jan 2026 (first class). After the that, no refunds are allowed."}],Sq=[{id:"language-and-prerequisites",question:"Language and Prerequisites?",answer:"The course will be taught in Hindi. Technical terms will remain in English. No prior programming experience is required. Basic computer skills and the willingness to learn are enough and explore beyond the course."},{id:"class-recordings",question:"Will I get recordings if I miss a class?",answer:"Yes. Every session is recorded and uploaded within 3-4 hours. You can watch it anytime until the course access is active."},{id:"timings",question:"What are the class timings?",answer:"Live classes are held on every Monday & Wednesday at 9:00 PM IST."},{id:"course-access",question:"How long will I have access to the course content?",answer:"You get 3 years (1095 days) of access to all videos, notes, and resources."},{id:"masterji",question:"What is MasterJi and community?",answer:"MasterJi is our in-house platform where you track progress, give assignments to submit, provide code feedback and build projects. The community is hosted inside the MasterJi app. You will receive access before the cohort starts."},{id:"job-guarantee",question:"Is this course job-guaranteed?",answer:"No, this course does not offer a job guarantee. We provide a skill guarantee and make you capable enough to find opportunities on your own. If any referrals come during the cohort, they will be given only to selected high-performing learners inside MasterJi"},{id:"devices",question:"How many devices can I access the course on?",answer:"You can access the course on 2 devices—one laptop and one mobile. If the system detects account sharing, the account will be banned without notice, and course access will be permanently lost"},{id:"payment-methods",question:"What payment methods are supported?",answer:"All major payment options including UPI apps, Debit/ Credit cards, Netbanking from leading banks and popular wallets."},{id:"emi-options",question:"Are loan & EMI options available?",answer:"We do not recommend taking loan or EMI for this course as a student. If your finances are tight right now, you can start learning from our YouTube channel ChaiAurCode for free, it already covers a lot."},{id:"refund-policy",question:"What is the refund policy?",answer:"As you are a working professional, you will be taking decisions on system, you need to take this decision seriously too as there are no refunds. We trust your decision."}],kq=[{id:"language-and-prerequisites",question:"Language and Prerequisites?",answer:"The course will be taught in Hindi with technical terms in English. Basic JavaScript understanding is required before joining the cohort. React fundamentals will be revised during the course, but this is not a beginner-level JavaScript program."},{id:"class-recordings",question:"Will I get recordings if I miss a class?",answer:"Yes. Every session is recorded and uploaded within 3-4 hours. You can watch it anytime until the course access is active."},{id:"timings",question:"What are the class timings?",answer:"Live classes are held on every Saturday & Sunday at 11:00 AM IST."},{id:"course-access",question:"How long will I have access to the course content?",answer:"You get 3 years (1095 days) of access to all videos, notes, and resources."},{id:"masterji",question:"What is MasterJi and community?",answer:"MasterJi is our in-house platform where you track progress, give assignments to submit, provide code feedback and build projects. The community is hosted inside the MasterJi app. You will receive access before the cohort starts."},{id:"job-guarantee",question:"Is this course job-guaranteed?",answer:"No, this course does not offer a job guarantee. We provide a skill guarantee and make you capable enough to find opportunities on your own. If any referrals come during the cohort, they will be given only to selected high-performing learners inside MasterJi"},{id:"devices",question:"How many devices can I access the course on?",answer:"You can access the course on 2 devices—one laptop and one mobile. If the system detects account sharing, the account will be banned without notice, and course access will be permanently lost"},{id:"payment-methods",question:"What payment methods are supported?",answer:"All major payment options including UPI apps, Debit/ Credit cards, Netbanking from leading banks and popular wallets."},{id:"emi-options",question:"Are loan & EMI options available?",answer:"We do not recommend taking loan or EMI for this course as a student. If your finances are tight right now, you can start learning from our YouTube channel ChaiAurCode for free, it already covers a lot."},{id:"refund-policy",question:"What is the refund policy?",answer:"You can request a refund only upto 02nd May 2026 (first class). After the that, no refunds are allowed."}],Tq=[{id:"language-and-prerequisites",question:"Language and Prerequisites?",answer:"The course is taught in Hindi with technical terms in English. You should be comfortable writing JavaScript and using Node.js. No prior AI/ML background is required - we build the mental model from first principles."},{id:"stack",question:"What stack does this cohort use?",answer:"JavaScript / TypeScript on Node.js 20+ (ESM). We work with OpenAI, Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini, Ollama for local LLMs, Qdrant for vectors, Neo4j for graph memory, BullMQ for queues, Langfuse for observability, and MCP for the industry protocol layer."},{id:"class-recordings",question:"Will I get recordings if I miss a class?",answer:"Yes. Every session is recorded and uploaded within 3-4 hours. You can watch it anytime until your course access is active."},{id:"course-access",question:"How long will I have access to the course content?",answer:"You get 2 years (730 days) of access to all videos, notes, code and resources."},{id:"projects",question:"What projects will I build?",answer:"Streaming ChatGPT clone, Qdrant RAG service, PageIndex retrieval system, LLM Wiki, NotebookLM clone, AI PPT maker, hand-rolled Claude-Code-style CLI agent, voice agent, GitHub PR review bot, personal memory app, and your own MCP server - among others."},{id:"job-guarantee",question:"Is this course job-guaranteed?",answer:"No, this course does not offer a job guarantee. We provide a skill guarantee and make you capable enough to find opportunities on your own. If any referrals come during the cohort, they will be given only to selected high-performing learners inside MasterJi."},{id:"devices",question:"How many devices can I access the course on?",answer:"You can access the course on 2 devices - one laptop and one mobile. If the system detects account sharing, the account will be banned without notice, and course access will be permanently lost."},{id:"payment-methods",question:"What payment methods are supported?",answer:"All major payment options including UPI apps, Debit/ Credit cards, Netbanking from leading banks and popular wallets."},{id:"emi-options",question:"Are loan & EMI options available?",answer:"We do not recommend taking loan or EMI for this course as a student. If your finances are tight right now, you can start learning from our YouTube channel ChaiAurCode for free, it already covers a lot."},{id:"refund-policy",question:"What is the refund policy?",answer:"You can request a refund only up to the first class (29th June, 2026) of the cohort. After that, no refunds are allowed."}],_q=[{id:"language-and-prerequisites",question:"Language and Prerequisites?",answer:"The course will be taught in Hindi and English mix. Technical terms will remain in English. No prior programming experience is required. Basic computer skills and the willingness to learn are enough and explore beyond the course."},{id:"course-access",question:"How long will I have access to the course content?",answer:"You get 4 years (1461 days) of access to all videos, notes, and resources."},{id:"job-guarantee",question:"Is this course job-guaranteed?",answer:"No, this course does not offer a job guarantee. We provide a skill guarantee and make you capable enough to find opportunities on your own."},{id:"devices",question:"How many devices can I access the course on?",answer:"You can access the course on 2 devices - one laptop and one mobile. If the system detects account sharing, the account will be banned without notice, and course access will be permanently lost."},{id:"payment-methods",question:"What payment methods are supported?",answer:"All major payment options including UPI apps, Debit/ Credit cards, Netbanking from leading banks and popular wallets."},{id:"emi-options",question:"Are loan & EMI options available?",answer:"We do not recommend taking loan or EMI for this course as a student. If your finances are tight right now, you can start learning from our YouTube channel ChaiAurCode for free, it already covers a lot."},{id:"refund-policy",question:"What is the refund policy?",answer:"Yes. We offer a 3-day, no-questions-asked refund from the date of purchase. After 3 days, refunds are not available. Once approved, the refund will be processed within 3–5 business days."}],H5="/assets/black-2-BQlauZxh.webp",z5="/assets/white-2-pi8ziUjj.webp",KT="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20width='437'%20height='59'%20viewBox='0%200%20437%2059'%20fill='none'%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3e%3cpath%20d='M54.6051%2058.8672V39.3033H23.3028V58.8672H1.18325e-05V0.00147775H23.3028V19.4785H54.6051V0.00147775H77.908V58.8672H54.6051ZM83.2588%2058.8672V0.00147775H106.562V58.8672H83.2588ZM136.702%2058.8672V21.3914H108.964V0.00147775H187.742V21.3914H159.918V58.8672H136.702ZM208.514%2058.8672