haiCode LMS",tagline:"Cohorts & Courses",description:"Watch videos and get links to join live classes. Your central hub for structured learning and community engagement.",platforms:["Web","Mobile"],link:"https://courses.chaicode.com/learn",mobileLinks:{ios:"https://apps.apple.com/in/app/chaicode/id6504993143",android:"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chaicode.courses"},badgeClass:"bg-[#f5a52433] text-[#c4841d] dark:text-[#f9c97c]"},{id:"masterji",name:"MasterJi",tagline:"Community Platform",description:"Submit assignments, participate in peer reviews, access townhall chats and audio spaces. Connect with fellow learners.",platforms:["Web","Mobile"],link:"https://masterji.co",mobileLinks:{ios:"https://apps.apple.com/by/app/masterji-learn-code/id6753772146",android:"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chaicode.masterji"},badgeClass:"bg-[#006FEE33] text-[#005bc4] dark:text-[#66aaf9]"},{id:"pr-masterji",name:"PR MasterJi",tagline:"Code Reviews",description:"Exclusively for cohort students. Get detailed code reviews and feedback from peers and instructors.",platforms:["Web"],link:"#",badgeClass:"bg-[#7828c833] dark:bg-[#9353d333] text-[#6020a0] dark:text-[#ae7ede]",hidden:!0},{id:"timearena",name:"TimeArena",tagline:"Consistency Tracker",description:"Personal time tracking with community features and socket overflow for instant answers. Build your learning streak.",platforms:["Web"],link:"https://timearena.in",badgeClass:"bg-[#f3126033] dark:bg-[#f3126033] text-[#c20e4d] dark:text-[#f871a0]"},{id:"chaityper",name:"ChaiTyper",tagline:"Typing Practice",description:"Improve your typing speed with code-focused exercises. Practice typing with real code snippets.",platforms:["Web"],link:"https://typer.chaicode.com",badgeClass:"bg-[#7828c833] dark:bg-[#9353d333] text-[#6020a0] dark:text-[#ae7ede]"},{id:"labs",name:"Labs",tagline:"Practice Arena",description:"Master multiple technologies through hands-on practice. A focused environment to practice, experiment, and grow your skills.",platforms:["Web"],link:"https://sql.chaicode.com",badgeClass:"bg-[#d4d4d866] dark:bg-[#71717a33] text-[#52525b] dark:text-[#d4d4d8]"},{id:"freeapi",name:"FreeAPI",tagline:"Open Source",description:"Open source API collection for learning and practice. Perfect for building real-world projects and testing.",platforms:["Web"],link:"https://freeapi.app",badgeClass:"bg-[#17c96433] dark:bg-[#74dfa233] text-[#12a150] dark:text-[#74dfa2] font-bold"},{id:"ui-vault",name:"UI Vault",tagline:"Project Components",description:"Central Repo for complete project pages. Now you can focus on building your project and not worrying about the UI.",platforms:["Web"],link:"https://ui.chaicode.com/",badgeClass:"bg-[#d4d4d866] dark:bg-[#71717a33] text-[#52525b] dark:text-[#d4d4d8]"},{id:"chaidocs",name:"ChaiDocs",tagline:"Documentation",description:"Comprehensive documentation for all ChaiCode products and learning resources. Your knowledge base.",platforms:["Web"],link:"https://docs.chaicode.com",badgeClass:"bg-[#006FEE33] text-[#005bc4] dark:text-[#66aaf9]"},{id:"udemy",name:"Udemy Courses",tagline:"English Courses",description:"Comprehensive courses in English for self-paced learning. Access our full catalog on Udemy platform.",platforms:["Web","Mobile"],link:"https://www.udemy.com/user/hitesh-choudharycom/",mobileLinks:{ios:"https://apps.apple.com/app/udemy-online-video-courses/id562413829",android:"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.udemy.android"},badgeClass:"bg-[#f5a52433] text-[#c4841d] dark:text-[#f9c97c]"}],kw={labs:[{src:"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/html5/html5-original.svg",alt:"HTML"},{src:"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/css3/css3-original.svg",alt:"CSS"},{src:"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg",alt:"JavaScript"},{src:"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg",alt:"Python"},{src:"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/numpy/numpy-original.svg",alt:"NumPy"},{src:"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg",alt:"PostgreSQL"}]},Tw=[{name:"Akshat Sharma",username:"aksh24_exe",content:`Over just 2 days, we dove deep into Networking concepts, Zoom, TCP/UDP, and DNS to understand how the internet connects and powers the world.
Huge shoutout to chaicode by @Hiteshdotcom and @piyushgarg_dev for breaking down these complex topics into simple explanations!`,avatar:"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1905287751299112960/x6aktW_9_400x400.jpg",href:"https://x.com/aksh24_exe/status/1878711261506294158",tag:["webdev"]},{name:"Nandan Manna",username:"coder_nandan",content:"Today's class was absolutely awesome! Learned how to build custom promises  Big thanks to @piyushgarg_dev and @Hiteshdotcom  for making it so engaging and insightful. Grateful for such amazing teachers!",avatar:"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1910193269763428352/CUmDipJe_400x400.png",href:"https://x.com/coder_nandan/status/1894456091788152957",tag:["webdev"]},{name:"Renil.tsx",username:"renilgarala",content:`Learn how the execution context works with high-level and low-level design.
This live class went on for over 3 hours. “Itna to college ki class bhi attend nahi ki!” But @Hiteshdotcom sir @piyushgarg_dev sir, I'm ready to attend a 4-5 hour class.`,avatar:"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1960048208954171392/xib0TRlD_400x400.jpg",href:"https://x.com/renilgarala/status/1893727198902726782",tag:["webdev"]},{name:"Levi",username:"SOURISH512394",content:`learned about Proxy, a topic that's often overlooked in many courses, but @Hiteshdotcom made it so easy to understand. Huge thanks to @piyushgarg_dev for breaking down Promises and explaining .then, .catch, and .finally so clearly
Ab thora late night grind karna parega!`,avatar:"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1887607723904339968/LNF9DOIx_400x400.jpg",href:"https://x.com/SOURISH512394/status/1894102132082561487",tag:["webdev"]},{name:"Ansh Kotnala",username:"AnshdotDev",content:`What a session in the Web Dev cohort! Started with a JS machine coding question, built a project using Date in JS, and then nailed Promises!
Big thanks to @Hiteshdotcom  & @piyushgarg_dev  for making everything so fun & easy!
Feeling pumped!`,avatar:"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1869666226408161280/oDfhGeNe_400x400.jpg",href:"https://x.com/AnshdotDev/status/1894098750852710693",tag:["webdev"]},{name:"Farhan Khan",username:"FarhanK43883",content:`Today I am very proud of myself because I designed my first responsive web page and I am very happy
